This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks related to facial attribute transfer, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image processing and manipulation, which could also place it under multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) categories.
